The bird entangled itself in the net.

The country became entangled in a grave economic crisis.
该国陷入了严重的经济危机。

陷入了阴谋圈套
They became entangled in dishonest business dealings.
他们陷入了不正当的商业交易之中。
(与坏人)交往，与…有牵连(with):
It looks as if he has been entangled with the bad woman.
看来他与那个坏女人有来往。
to get entangled with
an undesirable woman
